    • roundInteger

      public static int roundInteger(int integer, int floor)
      Round an integer to nearest multiple of floor. If 14 is the integer and 9 is the floor then method will return 18 or if the floor is same and integer is 13 it will return 9 not 18 because remainder between floor and integer is greater.
      Parameters:
      integer - int to be rounded
      floor - int to be rounded multiple of
      Returns:
      rounded integer
